snippet.textDisplay: I've been there once maybe 10 years ago with two friends. We were in our early 20s and not fanitic clubbers of techno lovers. But we heard about this famous club so we wanted tot check it out. When we were in the line there were two good looking girls in front of us. We asked if we could join them because we thought that would increase or chance to get in. They didn't want to join us but joined another group of guys that looked way cooler than us. They were right in front of us and when we got to the bouncer we saw that they got rejected. Our nerves must have been clearly visible  but when me and my friends got to the bouncer,  he pointed to the door and said 'come in'!! When we entered the club I looked behind me and saw one of the girls looking at us with a very sad face and disbelief in her eyes. Best night ever!
